      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a showroom-quality 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. This example features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, maintaining perfect compression and factory-spec vacuum routing. The front-midship layout ensures a perfect 50:50 weight distribution, complemented by a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical turn-in precision. The exterior retains its original high-gloss finish, while the interior remains a time capsule of driver-centric ergonomics. Mechanically unmodified and meticulously maintained, this FD represents a rare opportunity to own a survivor with impeccable apex seal integrity and thermal management systems.",
